    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><salute>D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Sir</salute></opener>
                <p>I received the account of poor <persName ref="pe0022">Ramsay</persName> &amp;
                    send my melancholy thanks. my last will inform you the <rs ref="ar0008">print</rs> is to sell for 5<hi rend="superscript">s</hi> of which <persName ref="pe0192">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Elliot</persName> is to have
                        1<hi rend="superscript">s</hi>â€”<hi rend="superscript">d</hi>6. I scarce
                    think <sic>it will worth </sic>advertising. c<hi rend="superscript">d</hi> it be
                    announced on the outside leaf of a magazine. or at most once advertised in two
                    different papers. they will be sent to <hi rend="underline">you</hi> by the
                    coach.</p>
                <p>The celts are too common to be drawn. I only beg to know <hi rend="underline">was
                        it Gilt or not</hi>?</p>
                <closer><salute>y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> most obed<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> Serv<hi rend="superscript">t</hi></salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">T.Pennant</persName></signed>
                    <dateline>Jan. 19<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> 1779</dateline></closer>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p><unclear reason="illegible">19</unclear></p>
            </div>
